    "Overall, it is a strong response but with a few areas for improvement.",
    "Automated Feedback for Short Answer ScoringIn Table 7, we present feedback for a 1-point response to item 10.",
    "We selected this particular response because model feedback was typical of what we observed for other items and score points.For item 10, to get full credit (2 points), the student had to (1) \"describe how [a chosen color] might affect the inside of the doghouse\" and (2) \"use results from the experiment to support [their] description.\"",
